snippet.title: Rocket Bot Royale - Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Playable NOW online at https://rocketbotroyale.winterpixel.io/ Rocket Bot Royale is a frantic free to play Battle Royale set on destructible, sinking islands. Fire rockets from your highly maneuverable custom robo-tank to eliminate the competition using advanced tactics and powerful weapons! 
Coming soon to PC and Mobile.
